# Frontend & View Standards

## ERB Views

- Gunakan `icon(:nama_icon)` dari ApplicationHelper, bukan emoji
- `content_for(:breadcrumbs)` untuk breadcrumb di layout
- `render "shared/pagination"` dengan `total_pages`, `current_page`
- Class: `card`, `stat-card`, `btn btn-primary`, `badge badge-<status>`

## Stimulus Controllers

- Naming: `*_controller.js`, register dengan kebab-case
- Value: `data-*-value`, Target: `data-*-target`
- `connect()`, `disconnect()` untuk setup/teardown

## CSS

- Variabel: `--primary-500`, `--color-text`, `--radius-lg`
- Dark mode: `[data-theme="dark"]`
- Animasi: `fadeInUp`, `slideInRight`, `animate-fade-in-up`
- Jangan inline style kecuali dinamis (width, --ring-percent)
